{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MwXDoXYxA3esW1KxnPrP4n","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile the comprehensive report:\n\n## CoinflipMatch On-Chain Account Layout\n\n### Program ID\n```\nBdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\n```\n\nSource: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/lib.rs` (line 9)\n\n---\n\n### CoinflipMatch Account Structure\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs` (lines 18–61)\n\n**Total Size**: 8 bytes (Anchor discriminator) + 238 bytes (InitSpace) = **246 bytes**\n\nThe account uses `#[derive(InitSpace)]`, which automatically calculates the size. Here's the exact field layout:\n\n| Offset | Field | Type | Size (bytes) | Description |\n|--------|-------|------|--------------|-------------|\n| 0–7 | *(discriminator)* | — | 8 | Anchor program discriminator |\n| 8–39 | `creator` | Pubkey | 32 | Match creator's wallet |\n| 40–71 | `opponent` | Pubkey | 32 | Opponent's wallet (Pubkey::default() if empty) |\n| 72–103 | `server` | Pubkey | 32 | Server co-signer (set at create_match) |\n| 104 | `tier` | u8 | 1 | Tier index (0–7) |\n| 105–112 | `entry_amount` | u64 | 8 | Entry in lamports (derived from tier) |\n| 113 | `creator_side` | u8 | 1 | Creator's choice: 0=Heads, 1=Tails |\n| 114 | `phase` | u8 | 1 | Current phase (see Phase Constants below) |\n| 115–146 | `commitment` | [u8; 32] | 32 | SHA256(server_secret) |\n| 147 | `algorithm_ver` | u8 | 1 | Fairness algorithm version |\n| 148–155 | `target_slot` | u64 | 8 | Slot for entropy reading (set on join) |\n| 156–163 | `resolve_deadline` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp deadline for settlement |\n| 164–195 | `result_hash` | [u8; 32] | 32 | Derived result hash (set on settle) |\n| 196 | `result` | u8 | 1 | Winning side: 0=Heads, 1=Tails (valid when settled) |\n| 197–228 | `winner` | Pubkey | 32 | Winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled) |\n| 229–236 | `created_at` | i64 | 8 | Unix timestamp when match created |\n| 237–244 | `nonce` | u64 | 8 | Match creation nonce (from player profile) |\n| 245 | `bump` | u8 | 1 | PDA bump seed |\n| 246 | `creator_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Creator voted for mutual refund |\n| 247 | `opponent_wants_refund` | bool | 1 | Opponent voted for mutual refund |\n\n**Total: 8 + 238 = 246 bytes**\n\n---\n\n### Phase Constants\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs` (lines 63–67)\n\n| Phase Name | Value | Description |\n|------------|-------|-------------|\n| `PHASE_WAITING` | 0 | Awaiting opponent to join |\n| `PHASE_LOCKED` | 1 | Both players in; awaiting settlement |\n| `PHASE_SETTLED` | 2 | Winner determined; funds distributed |\n| `PHASE_REFUNDED` | 3 | Match refunded (mutual or timeout) |\n\n---\n\n### Error Codes\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/error.rs`\n\nAnchor adds a 6000 base offset. Final code = 6000 + discriminant value.\n\n| Error | Discriminant | Final Code | Message |\n|-------|--------------|------------|---------|\n| `InvalidSide` | 100 | 6100 | Invalid side: must be 0 (Heads) or 1 (Tails) |\n| `InvalidTier` | 101 | 6101 | Invalid tier index |\n| `InvalidPhase` | 102 | 6102 | Match is not in the expected phase |\n| `InsufficientFunds` | 103 | 6103 | Insufficient funds for entry amount |\n| `CannotJoinOwnMatch` | 104 | 6104 | Creator cannot join their own match |\n| `ServerMismatch` | 105 | 6105 | Server key mismatch |\n| `CommitmentMismatch` | 106 | 6106 | Commitment does not match sha256(secret) |\n| `CannotCancel` | 107 | 6107 | Match can only be cancelled in WAITING phase |\n| `LockTimeoutNotElapsed` | 108 | 6108 | Lock timeout has not elapsed yet |\n| `EntropyTooShort` | 109 | 6109 | Entropy account must have at least 32 bytes |\n| `DeadlineNotReached` | 110 | 6110 | Resolve deadline has not been reached yet |\n| `AccountMismatch` | 111 | 6111 | Account key does not match expected value |\n| `NotParticipant` | 112 | 6112 | Caller is not a participant in this match |\n| `AlreadyVotedRefund` | 113 | 6113 | Caller has already voted for refund |\n\n---\n\n### PDA Seeds\n\n**Match Account**:\n```\nseeds = [b\"match\", creator_pubkey, nonce.to_le_bytes()]\n```\nThe nonce comes from the creator's PlayerProfile and ensures uniqueness across multiple matches by the same creator.\n\n---\n\n### Tier Entry Amounts\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/tiers.rs`\n\n| Tier Index | Tier Name | Entry Amount (lamports) | Entry (SOL) |\n|------------|-----------|------------------------|-------------|\n| 0 | Copper | 2,500,000 | 0.0025 |\n| 1 | Iron | 5,000,000 | 0.005 |\n| 2 | Bronze | 10,000,000 | 0.01 |\n| 3 | Silver | 50,000,000 | 0.05 |\n| 4 | Gold | 100,000,000 | 0.1 |\n| 5 | Platinum | 250,000,000 | 0.25 |\n| 6 | Diamond | 500,000,000 | 0.5 |\n| 7 | Emerald | 1,000,000,000 | 1.0 |\n\n---\n\n### CreateMatch Instruction\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/create_match.rs` (lines 11–39)\n\n**Accounts Required**:\n1. `creator` (signer, mut) — Match creator; funds the escrow\n2. `server` (signer) — Co-signer; validates commitment\n3. `coinflip_match` (init, mut, PDA) — The match account being created\n4. `config` (readonly, PDA) — Global config for pause checks\n5. `system_program` — Required for account creation\n\n**Instruction Parameters**:\n```rust\ncommitment: [u8; 32],  // SHA256(server_secret)\ntier: u8,              // 0–7 (selects entry_amount)\nside: u8,              // 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails\nnonce: u64,            // From creator's PlayerProfile.match_nonce\n```\n\n**Key Logic** (lines 41–91):\n- Validates `side` is 0 or 1\n- Validates `tier` is 0–7 and looks up `entry_amount` from tier table\n- Transfers `entry_amount` lamports from creator to match PDA (after rent)\n- Initializes match in `PHASE_WAITING` with all fields (lines 69–88)\n- The **`server` field is set to `ctx.accounts.server.key()`** (line 72)\n\n---\n\n### Settle Instruction\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/settle.rs` (lines 10–63)\n\n**Accounts Required**:\n1. `caller` (signer, mut) — Anyone with the secret; receives refunds\n2. `coinflip_match` (mut, PDA) — The match being settled\n3. `config` (readonly, PDA) — For treasury address\n4. `entropy` (UncheckedAccount) — 32+ bytes of entropy (mock slot hash)\n5. `treasury` (mut) — Receives fee; validated against `config.treasury`\n6. `creator` (mut) — Creator's wallet; receives winnings if they win\n7. `opponent` (mut) — Opponent's wallet; receives winnings if they win\n8. `creator_profile` (mut) — Creator's PlayerProfile on platform program (for CPI)\n9. `opponent_profile` (mut) — Opponent's PlayerProfile on platform program (for CPI)\n10. `platform_program` — For CPI to update profiles\n11. `system_program` — Standard\n\n**Instruction Parameters**:\n```rust\nsecret: [u8; 32]  // Server's secret (verified against commitment)\n```\n\n**Settlement Flow** (lines 65–175):\n- Reads entropy from the entropy account (first 32 bytes)\n- Verifies `secret` matches `commitment` (SHA256)\n- Derives result hash from `secret + entropy + match_key + algorithm_ver`\n- Extracts result: `result_side = result_hash[0] % 2` (0=Heads, 1=Tails)\n- Determines winner by comparing `result_side` with `creator_side`\n- Transfers fee to treasury; winner takes all remaining lamports\n- Updates both players' profiles via CPI (even refunding losers counts as a \"loss\")\n- Sets phase to `PHASE_SETTLED`\n- Zeros the match PDA\n\n---\n\n### Join Instruction\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs` (lines 10–32)\n\n**Accounts Required**:\n1. `opponent` (signer, mut) — Opponent joining\n2. `coinflip_match` (mut, PDA) — The match\n3. `config` (readonly, PDA) — Standard config\n4. `system_program` — Standard\n\n**Key Logic** (lines 34–65):\n- Validates match is in `PHASE_WAITING`\n- Validates opponent is not the creator\n- Transfers `entry_amount` from opponent to match PDA\n- Sets `opponent` field\n- Sets `target_slot = current_slot + ENTROPY_SLOT_OFFSET` (for entropy reading)\n- Sets `resolve_deadline = now + COINFLIP_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` (24 hours)\n- Transitions to `PHASE_LOCKED`\n\n**Timeout Constant** (from `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/timeout.rs`):\n```\nCOINFLIP_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS = 86_400 (24 hours)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Deserialization Reference (Off-Chain)\n\nTo deserialize a CoinflipMatch account off-chain:\n\n1. **Read discriminator** (bytes 0–7): Verify it matches Anchor's Coinflip program discriminator\n2. **Skip to byte 8** and read 238 bytes of account data\n3. **Field offsets** are in Borsh-serialized order (little-endian for multi-byte fields)\n4. **For phase checks**: Compare byte at offset 114 against phase constants (0, 1, 2, 3)\n5. **For result**: When phase == PHASE_SETTLED, read byte at offset 196 (0=Heads, 1=Tails)\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThis layout gives you exact byte offsets, phase discriminants, error codes, PDA seeds, tier mappings, and the complete instruction signatures for both creating and settling matches. The account is deterministically sized at 246 bytes and uses Borsh serialization."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ac188eb8857052905 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 45877\ntool_uses: 14\nduration_ms: 66100</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fa98a4f2-a7e5-449d-8951-5905b3595daa","uuid":"ef1038f6-0819-4e7d-833d-8d79dca9432a","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the CoinflipMatch on-chain account layout, specifically:\n1. The `state.rs` file showing match fields, phases/status enum values, and account size\